    slug: "gray-divorce-dividing-retirement-assets-qdro-401k-ira-pension",
    title: "Dividing Retirement Accounts in a Gray Divorce: QDROs, IRAs, Pensions, and Social Security",
    excerpt: "How 401(k)s, IRAs, pensions, and Social Security benefits get split when divorce happens after 70. The tax traps and how a QDRO actually works.",
    category: "tips-tricks",
    tags: ["gray-divorce", "qdro", "retirement-division", "ira-split", "pension-divorce"],
