    slug: "gray-divorce-dividing-family-home-sell-buyout-capital-gains",
    title: "Dividing the Family Home in a Gray Divorce: Sell, Buy Out, or Keep — and the Capital Gains Trap",
    excerpt: "Three ways to split the marital home after 70: sell and divide, one spouse buys out the other, or co-own. The capital gains rules that catch divorcing seniors.",
    category: "tips-tricks",
    tags: ["gray-divorce", "marital-home", "capital-gains", "real-estate-divorce", "home-buyout"],
    readTime: "11 min",
    thumbnailEmoji: "🏠",
